Battleplan
Endgoal: to be able to authenticate
- Figure out which endpoints we should use x
- We need an interface (login component) x
- Create a store and reducer to store the tokens x
- We have to create our actions
    - Action: send token to store
    - Thunk: send our email/password to the API and then send the token to store using action above


Redux general battleplan:
- Start with initial state
- Make the reducer
- Create your actions
- In components and start dispatching
- At some point you should be probably use a selector%